snippet.title: 'Glee' Cast Reunites! See Amber Riley, Matthew Morrison & More | News Flash | Entertainment Weekly
snippet.description:
On Thursday, Matthew Morrison, otherwise known as the beloved Mr. Schue, shared a photo with some of the cast and crew from Glee, who reunited for dinner in Los Angeles. Breaking bread with Morrison were Jane Lynch (Sue Sylvester), Naya Rivera (Santana), Heather Morris (Brittany), Amber Riley (Mercedes), Chris Colfer (Kurt), Kevin McHale (Artie), Jenna Ushkowitz (Tina), Becca Tobin (Kitty), and Vanessa Lengies (Sugar), plus choreographer Zachary Woodlee, script coordinator Aristotle Kousakis, and writers Matt Hodgson and Michael Hitchcock. Morrison’s wife Renee Morrison was also in attendance, along with their new baby, 4-month old Revel James Makai.

snippet.title: D&D Curse of Strahd Replay (Episode 10): The Amber Temple
snippet.description:
This is episode 10 in my Dungeons and Dragons Curse of Strahd replay. In this story the group heads over Solinka Pass and explores the secrets of the Amber Temple, trying to uncover a way to defeat Strahd once and for all.

The Characters:
(The Players)
Garo- Wood Elf Monk Cleric
Gouda- Gnome Wild Magic Sorcerer
Boshack- Lizardfolk Warlock
Krusk- Half- Orc Paladin

(Other NPCs)
Ireena- Woman that Strahd is after. We're trying to protect her.
Esmerelda- Vampire hunter. Trained by the famed Van Richten. 
Ismark- Ireena's Brother. 
Mordenkainen- Famous wizard who fought Strahd von Zarovitch a year ago and lost. Was in hiding.
Van Ricten- Famed vampire hunter.
Victor- Son the Baron Vallakovitch. Was making a teleportation circle in his attic, trying to escape from Barovia.


Music Credits: (All music from the Youtube Audio Library)
"From Russia With Love" by Huma-Huma
"Dreams Become Real" by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution license (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/...)
Source: http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-...
Artist: http://incompetech.com/
